00:34:13.918 --> 00:34:16.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have really changed, Ryoma.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:34:18.122 --> 00:34:19.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
