446
00:34:40.478 --> 00:34:43.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with guns that you sold!</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:34:45.716 --> 00:34:48.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm doing this</c.bg_transparent>
