449
00:34:54.258 --> 00:34:56.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is war the only way to unite the country?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:35:00.398 --> 00:35:02.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
