464
00:35:59.123 --> 00:36:01.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't change the world otherwise!</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:36:03.761 --> 00:36:05.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everyone who wages war</c.bg_transparent>

