00:36:35.726 --> 00:36:37.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I may seem special.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:36:40.198 --> 00:36:41.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But…</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:44.068 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am also</c.bg_transparent>

