00:36:47.004 --> 00:36:49.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>fighting to make this a better country!</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:37:01.085 --> 00:37:03.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In my own way… but still.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:37:10.194 --> 00:37:13.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be afraid. I'm just a town doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

