513
00:42:00.284 --> 00:42:01.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>After that,</i></c.bg_transparent>

514
00:42:02.386 --> 00:42:04.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
