517
00:42:22.339 --> 00:42:24.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right now, Mr. Glover.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:42:27.645 --> 00:42:29.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Something began to become</i></c.bg_transparent>
