526
00:43:08.719 --> 00:43:09.954 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Minakata.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:43:16.627 --> 00:43:18.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tomorrow,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I will be returning to my hometown.</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:43:19.630 --> 00:43:20.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
