529
00:43:24.568 --> 00:43:25.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that so?</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:43:26.470 --> 00:43:28.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been</c.bg_transparent>
