534
00:43:40.384 --> 00:43:42.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Could it be…</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:43:43.387 --> 00:43:45.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
