540
00:44:01.005 --> 00:44:04.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Mr. Tanaka, aside from the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>mujinto</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>,</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:44:04.575 --> 00:44:07.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you've also made medical instruments,</c.bg_transparent>
